/a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/the-funky-side-of-life.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/thefunkyside.jpg" alt="The Funky Side of Life / Yesterdays New Quintet" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/06/the-funky-side-of-life.php">The Funky Side of Life<br />Yesterdays New Quintet</a></h4><p>madlib名義の中でも特に好きなYNQの2ndです。ファンク・レアグルーブの名曲を、madlibと名だたるセッションミュージシャンがコラボして作り上げたというお得な一品になっています。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000AP2ZOY?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000AP2ZOY" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'The Funky Side of Life-Yesterdays New Quintet']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fwanda-vidal%252Fid79766329%253Fi%253D79766133%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30 ARTISTNAME: Y" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'The Funky Side of Life-Yesterdays New Quintet']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div></div>

